# SC MPS Display  

## Directory Structure  
.  
|-- README  
|-- RELEASE_NOTES  
|-- sc_mps_gui.bash  
`-- gui/  
    |-- mps_gui_main.ui  
    |-- mps_gui_main.py  
    |-- mixins/  
    |   |-- __init__.py  
    |   |-- summary.py  
    |   |-- logic.py  
    |   `-- selection_detail.py  
    |-- models/  
    |   |-- __init__.py  
    |   |-- mps_model.py  
    |   `-- logic_model.py
